    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of the people of Bénin, particularly of the modern inhabitants. For the style and culture of the more ancient people of southern Nigeria, use "Benin."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
